transmit.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the PRICE_ADMIN_ROLE
├─ it should revert
└─ when the caller has the PRICE_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when the unverified reports list is empty
   ├─ it should revert
   └─ when the unverified reports list is not empty
      ├─ when the report's feed id is not allowlisted
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the report's feed id is allowlisted
         ├─ when the report's observation timestamp is older than the staleness threshold
         │  └─ it should revert
         └─ when the report's observation timestamp is more recent than the staleness threshold
            ├─ when the report's scaled price is zero
            │  └─ it should revert
            └─ when the report's scaled price is not zero
               ├─ when the verified report price is not 18 decimals
               │  └─ it should scale the price to 18 decimals
               ├─ it should set price info
               └─ it should emit a PriceTransmitted event
